pds.cdf
Class CDRecord

java.lang.Object
  pds.cdf.Record
      pds.cdf.CDRecord

public class CDRecord
extends Record

CDF Descriptor Record (CDR). The CDR contains general information about the CDF. Defined in Section 2.2 of CDF specification.

Author:
tking
